item.title: About
item.description: My name is Bury Moneylow, welcome to my crib. This is hopefully going to be my new personal blog I’ll push on Github and all that. Seeing how all my previous efforts of writing a blog led nowhere really, I’m a bit skeptical about this but sure look, hope springs eternal. The plan is to write about anything that comes to my mind, coding or other IT-related stuff, music - making or consuming it - and all that jazz.
